flowchart TD
  A[Trigger: PO change request from procurement user or supplier, or automated signal from supplier performance / shortage propagation (Kinaxis/SAS) indicating need to modify an open PO.]
  A --> N1[Stream: DDM/Crawlers - Ingest change request and relevant PO + contract data]
  N1 --> N2[Stream: STREAMS - Analyze impact on delivery risk, inventory, and spend]
  N2 --> N3{PB: Agent Team - Agentic synthesis and recommendation generation}
  N3 -->|Primary| N4[PB: Process Builder / CWB Lifecycle - Route recommendation for approval and capture decision]
  N4 --> N5[PB: Remote Functions / Notification - Execute approved PO changes and notify stakeholders]
  N5 --> N6[PB: UI Screen / Subject Areas - Surface audit trail and review outcome]
  N6 --> Z1[Outcome: PO updates are applied in S4 for approved changes, exceptions are routed for manual review, delivery and spend risk are mitigated through coordinated coordination with Kinaxis signals and procurement approvals, and stakeholders are notified.]
  N3 -->|Change exceeds financial or contractu...| B1[Process Builder routes to multi-level approvals via CWB Lifecycle (escalate to finance / legal)]
  B1 --> O1[Outcome: Change held pending required approvals; audit trail captured; decision later triggers Remote Functions on approval]
  O1 --> End[End]
  N3 -->|High delivery risk / shortage urgency...| B2[Agent Team recommends expedited approval path and optional partial acceptance (e.g., split shipments); Process Builder triggers expedited notifications and prioritizes approval]
  B2 --> O2[Outcome: PO modified to mitigate stockout risk (expedite or increase qty) with approvals captured post-facto if within policy]
  O2 --> End[End]
  N3 -->|Supplier rejects proposed change or c...| B3[Agent Team surfaces alternatives (alternative suppliers, interim transfers) and creates exception CWB for procurement negotiation]
  B3 --> O3[Outcome: Negotiation workflow initiated; PO change not written until negotiated resolution; stakeholders alerted]
  O3 --> End[End]
  Z1 --> End[End]